      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 15:53:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>长期收益率与短期收益率差距扩大，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/treasuries-fall-as-long-rates-expand-gap-over-short-maturities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于假期缩短的交易时间，美国国债承受压力，因为投资者仍然对将现金存入十年或更长时间到期的美国政府债券持谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/treasuries-fall-as-long-rates-expand-gap-over-short-maturities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 15:48:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行起诉美联储，质疑压力测试实施方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/banks-sue-fed-seeking-public-input-on-stress-testing-process</link>
      <description><![CDATA[银行行业组织在一项诉讼中表示，美联储在设计银行压力测试时没有考虑到适当的公众意见，该诉讼旨在迫使美联储向公众公开测试设计意见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/banks-sue-fed-seeking-public-input-on-stress-testing-process</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 15:27:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场股市为 2024 年上涨做最后冲刺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/emerging-market-assets-advance-in-final-push-for-2024-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股市周二上涨，在亚洲科技股上涨和中国准备推出更多刺激措施的迹象的推动下，主要股市指数有望以近两位数的回报率结束今年的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/emerging-market-assets-advance-in-final-push-for-2024-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 10:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
